lee 2 (one creature); +21 vs. AC&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d8 + 11 damage.&lt;/p&gt;]] (⚔) <b>Slam</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Melee 2 (one creature); [[/roll 1d20+21[ vs. AC]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Slam&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Melee 2 (one creature); &lt;u&gt;+21 vs. AC&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 3d8 + 11#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;(⚔) &lt;b&gt;Slam&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 3d8 + 11 damage.&lt;/p&gt;]] <24.5>  damage.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Topple&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Requirement:&lt;/i&gt; The golem must be affected by wall form.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Close blast 5 (creatures in the blast); +19 vs. Fortitude&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 4d8 + 9 damage, and the golem pushes the target up to 3 squares and knocks it prone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Miss:&lt;/i&gt; Half damage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The golem is no longer affected by wall form and appears in an unoccupied space within or adjacent to the blast’s area.&lt;/p&gt;]] ᗕ <b>Topple</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Requirement:</i> The golem must be affected by wall form.</p><p><i>Attack:</i> Close blast 5 (creatures in the blast); [[/roll 1d20+19[ vs. Fortitude]#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Topple&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Attack:&lt;/i&gt; Close blast 5 (creatures in the blast); &lt;u&gt;+19 vs. Fortitude&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]</p><p><i>Hit:</i> [[/roll 4d8 + 9#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Topple&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Hit:&lt;/i&gt; 4d8 + 9 damage, and the golem pushes the target up to 3 squares and knocks it prone.&lt;/p&gt;]] <27>  damage, and the golem pushes the target up to 3 squares and knocks it prone.</p><p><i>Miss:</i> Half damage.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The golem is no longer affected by wall form and appears in an unoccupied space within or adjacent to the blast’s area.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Wall Form&lt;/b&gt; (polymorph) ✦ &lt;b&gt;At-Will&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect:&lt;/i&gt; The golem no longer occupies its current space and instead occupies the squares within a close wall 6. The squares must be unoccupied. While in this form, the golem is blocking terrain, is 3 squares high, and gains resist 20 to all damage. In addition, the golem can take no actions other than using topple or spending a free action to return to its normal form in an unoccupied space adjacent to a square of the wall.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Wall Form</b> (polymorph) ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p><i>Effect:</i> The golem no longer occupies its current space and instead occupies the squares within a close wall 6. The squares must be unoccupied. While in this form, the golem is blocking terrain, is 3 squares high, and gains resist 20 to all damage. In addition, the golem can take no actions other than using topple or spending a free action to return to its normal form in an unoccupied space adjacent to a square of the wall.</p></tr></td><tr><td><h4><b>Triggered</b></h4></td></tr><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:darkred;color:white;\"&gt;ᗕ &lt;b&gt;Collapse&lt;/b&gt; ✦ &lt;b&gt;Encounter&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Trigger:&lt;/i&gt; The golem is first bloodied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Effect (Free Action):&lt;/i&gt; The golem uses topple, even if it does not meet the power’s requirement. The golem is then removed from play, and any effects on it end. At the start of its next turn, the golem appears in an unoccupied space within or adjacent to the squares it last occupied.&lt;/p&gt;]] ᗕ <b>Collapse</b> ✦ <b>Encounter</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> The golem is first bloodied.</p><p><i>Effect (Free Action):</i> The golem uses topple, even if it does not meet the power’s requirement. The golem is then removed from play, and any effects on it end. At the start of its next turn, the golem appears in an unoccupied space within or adjacent to the squares it last occupied.</p></tr></td></table>",
